{"tid":2271424,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇連登仔日燈夜燈 真係燈到牙祖贏埋","createTime":"2020-11-04T14:09:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T12:08:11.000Z","uid":379666,"like":18,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cc911af32a6228d68d479329b136382af2c544c8","tid":2271424,"uid":379666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T14:09:56.000Z","msg":"恭喜連登仔求仁得仁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真係想知班人係度燈係咩心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個閪腦點解會覺得燈兩燈可以影響到隔住個海既國家<br />\n係咁有用隔離三峽爆左啦<br />\n班戇鳩只係想證明自己冇錯<br />\n講 a 贏，結果 a 贏，即係佢岩<br />\n講 a 贏，結果 b 贏，大家都想 b 贏，咁佢咪話自己係燈神<br />\n同成日話人炒車一樣，佢地唔係想件事，整體變好，佢地只係想證明自己冇錯<br />\n實際呢 d 人只係班連冇壞後果都唔敢落注既垃圾<br />\n呢 d 人只會做應聲蟲，唔敢下決定既廢柴"},{"pid":"9cc28b676bf8e1cb7b8cba3c1f0f524978c0edcc","tid":2271424,"uid":73381,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T14:11:22.000Z","msg":"樓主永遠睇得最清 但大部分連登仔不願面對"},{"pid":"cc221877a6bb864d8828b976c633435f19e1eba8","tid":2271424,"uid":312363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T14:11:42.000Z","msg":"兒登仔不願面對現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5abb31533b1e5e04932150e7084c7358bd367ad","tid":2271424,"uid":18271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T14:12:51.000Z","msg":"無燈到啦，終於中<br />\n成日都話拜登贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c6087287a1a807c34af13d6dba8317770f83d1b","tid":2271424,"uid":379666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9cc28b676bf8e1cb7b8cba3c1f0f524978c0edcc","tid":2271424,"uid":73381,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T14:11:22.000Z","msg":"樓主永遠睇得最清 但大部分連登仔不願面對"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T14:13:46.000Z","msg":"連登（cc台)只係一班失敗者 無膽匪類"},{"pid":"449272f03850ad5a7534e3f0adb2f524130cb04a","tid":2271424,"uid":52571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T14:13:54